{"TopicId":135967,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"VAB/SPH Editor","CreatedByName":"Moesly_Armlis","CreatedById":112247,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-03T18:45:04Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Moesly_Armlis","CreatedById":112247,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-03T18:45:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EBlack Outline Text\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLight colour text is washed out on light colour backgrounds.\u00A0 This will improve readability whether the background is dark or light.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022gNuWaSM.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/gNuWaSM.png\u0022 style=\u0022width:400px;height:224px;\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022kxCAoXa.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/kxCAoXa.png\u0022 style=\u0022width:400px;height:224px;\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ECOM\u0026amp;COT Alignment Indication.\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen centre of thrust is aligned with centre of mass have some indication.\u00A0 Currently I connect to the engine I-Beams that are repositioned and then try to eyeball it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe change colour of COT arrow with two variants; light for close, dark for spot on.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnother trick I did was to place engines on the I-Beam and this would raise the COT into the COM.\u00A0 Maybe have a method to gizmo the COT ball.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNew idea: Or lengthen the back end of the thrust vector until it extends through the COM ball.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022S0JCoXj.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/S0JCoXj.png\u0022 style=\u0022width:400px;height:224px;\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\npre release 1.1 (1183) COM COT COL icons disappear when in Subassemblies.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EStock Vessels\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSandbox should have option to exclude Stock Vessels.\u00A0 My sandbox projects start with the letter A (Yellowpage strategy) just to make them easier to find.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Svuyzrv.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/Svuyzrv.png\u0022 style=\u0022width:400px;height:224px;\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022XGc1K9I.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/XGc1K9I.png\u0022 style=\u0022width:400px;height:224px;\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe option is available in career.\u00A0 Just unhide the Allow Stock Vessel button for sandbox.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Ck3Xja7.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/Ck3Xja7.png\u0022 style=\u0022width:400px;height:224px;\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022QxmXqQD.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/QxmXqQD.png\u0022 style=\u0022width:400px;height:224px;\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-06T02:14:40Z\u0022 title=\u002204/06/2016 02:14  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 6, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by MoeslyArmlis\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}